80fc9d95-9ea2-43aa-9a95-3a9b1884a529	414ac7be-0234-4367-9912-fe073afdeffc	1	Baalvion for Manufacturing	{"slug": "manufacturing", "title": "Baalvion for Manufacturing", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "Industrial telemetry, operations visibility, and supply-chain integration — turning sensor data into uptime and throughput.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "Manufacturing & Industrial Technology | Baalvion", "keywords": ["manufacturing technology", "industrial IoT", "telemetry", "predictive maintenance", "Baalvion industries", "operations"], "description": "Baalvion builds industrial platforms: high-scale telemetry, real-time operations dashboards, predictive maintenance, and supply-chain integration."}, "customFields": {"faqs": [{"a": "Yes — our telemetry pipelines are sized for hundreds of sensors per site across many sites, with second-level latency into live dashboards.", "q": "Can you handle our sensor data volume?"}, {"a": "Trend-based anomaly detection over time-series data flags developing equipment issues early, so they can be addressed before causing downtime.", "q": "How does predictive maintenance work?"}, {"a": "Yes — we integrate operational data with supply-chain and logistics visibility, as in our [logistics control tower](/case-studies/logistics-control-tower).", "q": "Can you connect operations to our supply chain?"}, {"a": "Typically [automation](/services/automation), [cloud solutions](/services/cloud-solutions), and [AI solutions](/services/ai-solutions).", "q": "Which services apply to manufacturing?"}], "kind": "industry", "solutions": ["High-throughput telemetry ingestion and time-series storage", "Real-time dashboards and trend-based alerting", "Predictive signals to catch failures early", "Integrated supply-chain and logistics visibility"], "challenges": ["High-volume sensor data with no unified view", "Unplanned downtime that's discovered too late", "Disconnected operational and supply-chain systems", "Optimising throughput across sites"], "internalLinks": [{"href": "/case-studies/mining-operations-command-center", "anchor": "a real-time command center for mining operations"}, {"href": "/news/tech/observability-for-distributed-systems", "anchor": "observability"}, {"href": "/services/automation", "anchor": "automation"}, {"href": "/case-studies/logistics-control-tower", "anchor": "logistics control tower"}]}, "contentBlocks": [{"id": "blk-0", "type": "heading", "order": 0, "content": {"text": "Sector Overview", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-1", "type": "paragraph", "order": 1, "content": {"text": "Manufacturing generates enormous volumes of operational data — and historically wastes most of it. Sensors stream readings into isolated systems, problems surface only after they cause downtime, and no one has a unified operational picture. Baalvion turns that noise into decisions, as we did in [a real-time command center for mining operations](/case-studies/mining-operations-command-center)."}}, {"id": "blk-2", "type": "heading", "order": 2, "content": {"text": "Challenges", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-3", "type": "html", "order": 3, "content": {"html": "<ul><li><strong>Data volume:</strong> hundreds of sensors per site, with no single view.</li><li><strong>Downtime:</strong> failures discovered after the fact, not before.</li><li><strong>Disconnection:</strong> operations and supply chain rarely integrated.</li><li><strong>Throughput:</strong> optimising across multiple sites is hard without live data.</li></ul>"}}, {"id": "blk-4", "type": "heading", "order": 4, "content": {"text": "How Baalvion Helps", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-5", "type": "paragraph", "order": 5, "content": {"text": "We build high-throughput telemetry pipelines feeding real-time command centers, with trend-based alerting that catches developing problems early — the [observability](/news/tech/observability-for-distributed-systems) discipline applied to physical operations. We integrate supply chain and logistics for end-to-end visibility, connecting to capabilities like our [logistics control tower](/case-studies/logistics-control-tower)."}}, {"id": "blk-6", "type": "heading", "order": 6, "content": {"text": "Relevant Services", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-7", "type": "paragraph", "order": 7, "content": {"text": "Manufacturing engagements typically combine [automation](/services/automation), [cloud solutions](/services/cloud-solutions), and [AI solutions](/services/ai-solutions) for predictive maintenance, plus [enterprise software](/services/enterprise-software) to tie operations together."}}, {"id": "blk-8", "type": "heading", "order": 8, "content": {"text": "Outcomes", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-9", "type": "paragraph", "order": 9, "content": {"text": "Manufacturers gain a single live operational picture across sites, catch equipment issues before they cause downtime, and connect operations to the supply chain — improving uptime and throughput together."}}]}	67	State changed to published	2026-06-11 12:31:30.255+00
16834dca-b572-40e3-b9f2-e9a2aa4db5c7	e13e44d7-ce90-4968-b578-425b9aa37e2c	1	Baalvion for Real Estate	{"slug": "real-estate", "title": "Baalvion for Real Estate", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "Property, transactions, and asset platforms — high-value workflows with escrow, document integrity, and clean integrations.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "Real Estate & PropTech Solutions | Baalvion", "keywords": ["real estate technology", "proptech", "property platform", "escrow", "asset management", "Baalvion industries"], "description": "Baalvion builds proptech platforms for property, high-value transactions, and asset management — with escrow, document integrity, and trusted workflows."}, "customFields": {"faqs": [{"a": "Escrow-backed settlement on a single ledger holds funds until conditions are met, protecting all parties — the pattern from [our marketplace case study](/case-studies/luxury-commerce-marketplace).", "q": "How do you make high-value property transactions safe?"}, {"a": "Tamper-evident, append-only records mean contracts and documents can be verified and their history traced.", "q": "How is document integrity ensured?"}, {"a": "Yes — we build API-first so the full listing-to-close journey lives in one coherent platform.", "q": "Can you integrate listing, transaction, and finance systems?"}, {"a": "Typically [custom software development](/services/custom-software-development), [enterprise software](/services/enterprise-software), and [web development](/services/web-development).", "q": "Which services apply to real estate?"}], "kind": "industry", "solutions": ["Escrow-backed transaction settlement on one ledger", "Tamper-evident document and audit records", "Integrated listing-to-close workflows", "Durable, verifiable record-keeping"], "challenges": ["High-value, multi-party transactions that need trust", "Document-heavy workflows with integrity requirements", "Fragmented listing, transaction, and finance systems", "Long-lived records that must stay verifiable"], "internalLinks": [{"href": "/case-studies/luxury-commerce-marketplace", "anchor": "our luxury commerce marketplace"}, {"href": "/news/tech/api-first-architecture", "anchor": "API-first architecture"}, {"href": "/services/custom-software-development", "anchor": "custom software development"}, {"href": "/services/enterprise-software", "anchor": "enterprise software"}]}, "contentBlocks": [{"id": "blk-0", "type": "heading", "order": 0, "content": {"text": "Sector Overview", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-1", "type": "paragraph", "order": 1, "content": {"text": "Real estate transactions are high-value, multi-party, and document-heavy — exactly the conditions where trust and integrity matter most and manual processes fail. Baalvion brings the escrow, ledgering, and document-integrity patterns it built for commerce and finance to property and asset platforms."}}, {"id": "blk-2", "type": "heading", "order": 2, "content": {"text": "Challenges", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-3", "type": "html", "order": 3, "content": {"html": "<ul><li><strong>Trust:</strong> large sums move between parties who may not know each other.</li><li><strong>Documents:</strong> contracts and records must be tamper-evident and traceable.</li><li><strong>Fragmentation:</strong> listing, transaction, and finance tools rarely connect.</li><li><strong>Longevity:</strong> property records must remain verifiable for years.</li></ul>"}}, {"id": "blk-4", "type": "heading", "order": 4, "content": {"text": "How Baalvion Helps", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-5", "type": "paragraph", "order": 5, "content": {"text": "We apply escrow-backed settlement on a single ledger — the trust pattern from [our luxury commerce marketplace](/case-studies/luxury-commerce-marketplace) — add tamper-evident document and audit records, and integrate listing-to-close workflows the [API-first](/news/tech/api-first-architecture) way so the whole transaction lives in one coherent system."}}, {"id": "blk-6", "type": "heading", "order": 6, "content": {"text": "Relevant Services", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-7", "type": "paragraph", "order": 7, "content": {"text": "Real estate engagements combine [custom software development](/services/custom-software-development), [enterprise software](/services/enterprise-software), and [web development](/services/web-development), with [automation](/services/automation) for document and approval workflows."}}, {"id": "blk-8", "type": "heading", "order": 8, "content": {"text": "Outcomes", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-9", "type": "paragraph", "order": 9, "content": {"text": "Property platforms where high-value transactions are protected by escrow, documents are tamper-evident and traceable, the listing-to-close journey lives in one system, and records stay verifiable for the long term."}}]}	67	State changed to published	2026-06-11 12:31:30.268+00
278bfd0d-2f2d-441a-bb1b-df27b4d31134	3acfee2a-57a1-4f8e-b357-94f87e749d2a	1	Luxury Commerce Network	{"slug": "luxury-commerce-network", "title": "Luxury Commerce Network", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "Verified luxury brands and high-end trade operations on the Baalvion ledger.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "Luxury Commerce Network", "description": "Verified luxury brands and high-end trade operations on the Baalvion ledger."}, "customFields": {"kind": "project", "type": "Marketplace", "domain": "amarise.baalvion.com", "status": "Planned", "category": "Commerce", "priority": 6, "isFeatured": false}, "contentBlocks": []}	67	State changed to published	2026-05-30 12:20:32.582+00
c03abb37-d79a-4144-abe0-38874b057b6b	4a1f4ef1-5187-49d6-965a-458bdbb737e3	1	Quantum Computing Overview	{"slug": "quantum-computing-overview", "title": "Quantum Computing Overview", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "An introduction to quantum computing principles and their industrial applications.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "Quantum Computing Overview", "description": "An introduction to quantum computing principles and their industrial applications."}, "customFields": {}, "contentBlocks": [{"id": "blk-0", "type": "heading", "order": 0, "content": {"text": "What is Quantum Computing?", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-1", "type": "paragraph", "order": 1, "content": {"text": "Quantum computing leverages superposition and entanglement to perform computations intractable for classical machines."}}]}	67	State changed to published	2026-05-30 12:21:02.2+00
7dede364-7757-4ccf-a4ee-48ae8a4ad2cc	97ce4ff4-b4cf-4b22-927b-c9757ba334aa	1	Baalvion Reports 150% YoY Growth in Platform Transaction Volume for Q2 2024	{"slug": "q2-2024-growth", "title": "Baalvion Reports 150% YoY Growth in Platform Transaction Volume for Q2 2024", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "The company has exceeded all financial projections, citing strong enterprise adoption of its integrated trade OS and the successful rollout of its automated customs clearance module in key APAC markets.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "Baalvion Reports 150% YoY Growth in Platform Transaction Volume for Q2 2024", "description": "The company has exceeded all financial projections, citing strong enterprise adoption of its integrated trade OS and the successful rollout of its automated customs clearance module in key APAC markets."}, "customFields": {"date": "2024-07-20", "kind": "news-article", "imageId": "news-1-image"}, "contentBlocks": []}	67	State changed to published	2026-05-30 12:23:51.54+00
