93265747-6725-4dfd-861a-dc53bc0c0e00	2197908a-d912-4df1-8ae7-2f391a37558d	1	Q1 2026 Earnings Summary	{"slug": "q1-2026-earnings-summary", "title": "Q1 2026 Earnings Summary", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "Baalvion Group reports strong first-quarter results across all segments.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "Q1 2026 Earnings Summary", "description": "Baalvion Group reports strong first-quarter results across all segments."}, "customFields": {}, "contentBlocks": [{"id": "blk-0", "type": "heading", "order": 0, "content": {"text": "Financial Highlights", "level": 2}}, {"id": "blk-1", "type": "paragraph", "order": 1, "content": {"text": "Revenue grew 24% year-over-year, driven by the commerce and infrastructure segments."}}]}	67	State changed to published	2026-05-30 12:23:51.644+00
9f1d3a27-eeac-4f15-86c8-1f945ae84501	968838c7-e49a-4416-8604-cd8cc974b2a2	1	Imperialpedia Platform Overview	{"slug": "imperialpedia-platform-overview", "title": "Imperialpedia Platform Overview", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "Editorial content authored in the Baalvion admin platform now publishes straight to the Imperialpedia website through a single multi-site CMS.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "Baalvion Launches Unified Imperialpedia CMS Pipeline", "description": "How Baalvion publishes editorial content to Imperialpedia from one console."}, "customFields": {}, "contentBlocks": [{"id": "b0", "type": "paragraph", "order": 0, "content": {"text": "Baalvion today flipped on a unified content pipeline that lets editors publish to the Imperialpedia knowledge site directly from the central admin platform, with no engineering hand-off."}}, {"id": "b1", "type": "heading", "order": 1, "content": {"text": "One console, many sites", "level": 2}}, {"id": "b2", "type": "paragraph", "order": 2, "content": {"text": "Imperialpedia is registered as a website inside the shared CMS. Articles and news authored there flow through a draft → review → publish workflow and appear on the public site the moment they go live."}}, {"id": "b3", "type": "quote", "order": 3, "content": {"cite": "Baalvion Platform Team", "text": "Publishing should be a button, not a deploy. That is exactly what this delivers."}}, {"id": "b4", "type": "callout", "order": 4, "content": {"text": "Structured data (companies, markets, calculators) stays in the dedicated imperialpedia-service; the CMS owns the editorial layer.", "variant": "info"}}, {"id": "b5", "type": "paragraph", "order": 5, "content": {"text": "The same pipeline is being rolled out across the rest of the Baalvion network of sites."}}]}	67	State changed to published	2026-05-30 12:34:24.996+00
