0f6092c5-e219-4d15-a82b-9f04cf2183ac	b0ef123b-48ff-47a4-a672-7eb57b219229	1	How to Choose a Checking Account With No Hidden Fees	{"slug": "checking-account-no-hidden-fees", "title": "How to Choose a Checking Account With No Hidden Fees", "status": "published", "tagIds": [], "excerpt": "Monthly maintenance, overdraft, and ATM fees quietly erode your balance. A simple checklist to avoid them.", "seoMetadata": {"title": "How to Choose a Checking Account With No Hidden Fees", "description": "Monthly maintenance, overdraft, and ATM fees quietly erode your balance. A simple checklist to avoid them."}, "customFields": {}, "contentBlocks": [{"id": "b0", "type": "paragraph", "order": 0, "content": {"text": "Not all checking accounts are created equal. The cheapest headline can hide costly fees."}}, {"id": "b1", "type": "paragraph", "order": 1, "content": {"text": "Look for accounts that waive monthly maintenance fees with direct deposit, reimburse out-of-network ATM charges, and offer fee-free overdraft protection."}}, {"id": "b2", "type": "paragraph", "order": 2, "content": {"text": "Credit unions and online-only banks often beat large national banks on total cost of ownership."}}]}	9000099	State changed to published	2026-06-07 07:40:05.76+00
